      "type": "http",
      "documentation": "Trigger a workflow dispatch to start a build. Mirrors the GitHub Actions POST /repos/{owner}/{repo}/actions/workflows/{workflow_id}/dispatches endpoint. Returns 204 No Content immediately. A build-complete callback is sent to the URL in X-Callback-Url header (or http://localhost:3004/callback) after the configured latency (default 30s).",
